<svelte:options runes={true} />

<script lang="ts">
  import type { Component } from 'svelte';

  const PropsDemo: Component = {
    $props: {
      name: 'World',
      count: 0,
      showDetails: false
    },
    $state: {
      count: 0
    },
    $effect: () => {
      // This is just a placeholder effect
    },
    $render: () => {
      return {
        tag: 'div',
        children: [
          {
            tag: 'h1',
            attrs: { 'data-testid': 'name-display' },
            children: [Hello, ${$props.name}!]
          },
          {
            tag: 'p',
            attrs: { 'data-testid': 'count-display' },
            children: [Count: ${$state.count}]
          },
          {
            tag: 'button',
            attrs: { 'data-testid': 'increment-button' },
            children: ['Increment'],
            on: {
              click: () => {
                $state.count += 1;
              }
            }
          },
          {
            tag: 'div',
            attrs: { 'data-testid': 'details' },
            show: $props.showDetails,
            children: [
              {
                tag: 'p',
                children: [Name is ${$props.name}]
              },
              {
                tag: 'p',
                children: [Count is ${$state.count}]
              },
              {
                tag: 'p',
                children: [ShowDetails is ${$props.showDetails}]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      };
    }
  };
</script>
